snippet.title: Tidewoken Playtest Trailer
snippet.description:
The Tidewoken playtest starts on the 27th of January, request access now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1135220/Tidewoken/

Tidewoken is a multiplayer turn-based tactics game with strategic PvP and up to 4 player COOP.
Build your own characters out of 4 classes, 192 skills, and 30+ perks.
